00:02:14.989 --> 00:02:20.029
velocity.
It's over 250.

00:02:20.029 --> 00:02:25.109
When you feel comfortable with strafe jumps,
it's time to start practicing bhops.

00:02:25.109 --> 00:02:30.219
This time we're gonna strafe out and back
in again, but why?

00:02:30.219 --> 00:02:36.689
In order to get speed when bhopping, you need
to move left and right while following a single

00:02:36.689 --> 00:02:39.909
line.
The yellow line shows you which way you wanna/want

00:02:39.909 --> 00:02:46.549
to go and the red line shows you how you want
to move in the air to get more speed.

00:02:46.549 --> 00:02:51.959
