00:02:51.959 --> 00:02:59.879
to balance my speed and win extra velocity.
Remember to scroll up or down when landing.

00:02:59.879 --> 00:03:04.489
Make sure to practice on places where there's
higher or lower ground, because these little

00:03:04.489 --> 00:03:08.969
height differences will increase your speed
in most cases.

