00:03:20.329 --> 00:03:28.010
as long as you are using different heights
and still controlling your bhops and speed.

00:03:28.010 --> 00:03:32.239
So to summarize all this:
Think about your stafes in the air.

00:03:32.239 --> 00:03:37.010
Think about getting the velocity between 250
and 300 for best results.

00:03:37.010 --> 00:03:40.019
Remember to follow a single line for more
speed.

00:03:40.019 --> 00:03:48.049
And remember, also, that it's a lot harder
on 64 tick servers, so e.g. competitive matchmaking.

00:03:48.049 --> 00:03:53.180
